lass=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&#x3C;ReadonlyArray&#x3C;ReadT>></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-1\">Parameters</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locator</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | <a href=\"api/core/ProviderToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">ProviderToken</a>&#x3C;LocatorT></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>opts</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>object</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns-1\">Returns</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&#x3C;ReadonlyArray&#x3C;ReadT>></code></p>\n\n</div>\n    \n  \n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/contentChildren#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Query results are represented as a signal of a read-only collection containing all matched\nelements.</p>\n  <p>Further information is available in the <a href=\"api/core/contentChildren#usage-notes\">Usage Notes...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/contentChildren#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Create a children query in your component by declaring a\nclass field and initializing it with the <code><a href=\"api/core/contentChildren\" class=\"code-anchor\">contentChildren</a>()</code> function.</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({...})\nexport class TestComponent {\n  headerEl = <a href=\"api/core/contentChildren\" class=\"code-anchor\">contentChildren</a>&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>>('h');   // <a href=\"api/core/Signal\" class=\"code-anchor\">Signal</a>&#x3C;ReadonlyArray&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>>>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/ContentChildren\n - api/core/Directive\n - guide/signal-queries\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/ProviderToken\n - api/core/Signal\n - api/core/contentChildren#contentchildren\n - api/core/contentChildren#description\n - api/core/contentChildren#usage-notes\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/authoring/queries.ts#L213-L238\n-->"
